complete revelation of His will for the salvation of men.
They constitute the divine and only rule of Christian faith and practice.</td>
    <td class="w30text">2Tim 3:16, 17;<br> 2Pet 1:20,21</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="w2text">Man was originally created in the image and likeness of God</td>
